#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:2
#: b812d9ea087f471b83279ef605bf1916
msgid "开源硬件-小安派系列"
msgstr "Open-Source Hardware - AiPi Series"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:16
#: dea5bfe5f61c489aad99e01750047b60
msgid "小安派开发板能驱动60pin的屏幕吗"
msgstr "Can the AiPi development board drive a 60-pin screen?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:17
#: 3caf8ac8bf474e9dadacb7c0cb3c58a7
msgid "不能，开发板内部没有这么多引脚接到屏幕上"
msgstr ""
"No. The development board does not have enough internal pins connected to "
"the screen."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:20
#: ee8574c954c84a528746d4d363e26678
msgid "小安派开发板的屏幕和摄像头能同时使用吗"
msgstr ""
"Can the screen and camera of the AiPi development board be used at the same "
"time?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:21
#: 0ca38eacab9a47598edaad1e30a58d31
msgid ""
"不能同时使用，因为这两个外设都占用一些相同的引脚，同时使用会导致外设无法正常"
"工作"
msgstr ""
"No, they cannot be used at the same time, because these two peripherals "
"occupy some of the same pins. Using them simultaneously will cause the "
"peripherals to fail to work properly."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:24
#: 212c61fd8c4548a98ba23562f68faa1e
msgid "小安派-Eyes开发板有语音识别功能吗"
msgstr "Does the AiPi-Eyes development board have voice recognition?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:25
#: 91ddc680db0248c3825b36d106dc1484
msgid "没有，目前该板子没有集成语音识别功能"
msgstr "No. Currently, this board does not integrate voice recognition."
